 </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">διάνοια ἀχλύος γέμουσα</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.42c</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n18729.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ὑγρή</foreign> liquid emitted by cuttlefish, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:158\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.158</biblScope></bibl>.—Mostly poet., but used by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> </bibl> (v. supr.) and <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:367b:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mete.\">Mete.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">367b17</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg026:373b:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">373b12</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.): also in later Prose, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:34:11:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34.11.15</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:2:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.2.8</biblScope></bibl>, and <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> supr. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</bib